title: ALITOVE 20 Sets 3 Pin JST SM Male Female Plug LED Connector Cable 15cm 20awg wire for WS2812B WS2812 WS2811 SK6812 SK6812-RGBW LED Strip light
feature: Great 3 pin JST SM connectors for WS2812B WS2812 WS2811 SK6812 SK6812-RGBW LED strip light, Arduino and Raspberry Pi project.
It is good for whenever you have 3 wires you want to be able to plug and unplug.
The pigtails are pre-tinned making soldering easy.
The connector is reliable and safe, no loose, lightweight and beautiful appearance
Please check the colors of the wires and their respective polarities before connecting to your device(s).
description: These 3-wire cables are 150mm (5.9in) long and come as a set. One cable has a male JST SM type connector plug on the end. The other cable has a matching female JST SM type receptacle connector. They are good for whenever you have 3 wires you want to be able to plug and unplug. We like the solid and compact nature of these connectors and the latch that keeps the cable from coming apart easily. 100% Brand new and high quality 3pin connector cable Connect method: Male & Female ends push in Material: PVC plastic Length: 15cm approx (Single 3PIN connector) Core: 0.3mm (Single cable) Color: as picture shown Working temperature: -20~60° c Storage temperature: -30~95° c 20 pairs 3pin JST SM male and female connectors
